          <p class="text-slate mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "I could not rave any more about Jenna & ACE Accountable. She is so good at what she does, 
            I could not recommend her more than I already do, which is every chance I get! If you are 
            a small business, you need Jenna & ACE...it's really that simple!"
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal to-ocean rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              JK
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-midnight">John K.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate">Bloomfield, CT</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
